Why don't you replace <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> redneck</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> with [/i]poor white trash[/i].  Somehow these are popularly used but don't think for an instant that they don't have harmful effects.  They create a line, just like the word above.  The difference is that the harm done is in perceptions of those outside - and how they prejudge those that are cursed with this title.<br>
<br>
Ceru<br>
